features: Lightweight double-weave fabric is soft and warm next to skin but doesn’t trap heat; face is durable and treated with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish to shed moisture
Stretch fabric and design supports a wide range of movement
Two welted, high handwarmer pockets have cleanly finished zipper garages and are harness- and pack-compatible
Sleek, low-bulk, snag-resistant cuffs with stretch knit provide versatile coverage and comfort
Dual-adjust cord-lock system at hem seals in warmth
